			A long time ago they decided that they didn't like the direction things were going and made a small, simple, sensible change to the game.  They gave healing spells a reasonable amount of aggro.<br><br>If the cleric union hadn't threatened a walkout, we would have a much nicer game today.  No druid or shaman percentage heals would be needed or desired.  Players wouldn't have ridiculous amounts of hitpoints and bosses wouldn't hit like freight trains.<br><br>I expect you'd see a similar response from the warrior community today if you tried to take their toy away.
